description: For sale: $149,500. A beautiful 2 bedroom/2 bathroom condo in Roseville within minutes of downtown St Paul and Roseville Shopping Mall. The city bus line is a short distance from the condo development. The unit has newly updated with refurbished kitchen cabinets, newer appliances, new refrigerator, new carpet, new paint and laminate flooring. The Hamline House condos common amenities: park-like courtyard, indoor heated swimming pool, an exercise room, sauna, elevators, underground heated parking and a large community party room. This updated, spacious condo features a neutral color scheme and spacious master suite with tons of closet space. Move-in ready!

Recently sold: $178,100. Beautiful Roseville top floor 1-level condo ready to move in and enjoy. Central Park is across the street. Private porch with view of Lake Bennett. Abundant natural light captured by south windows & vaulted ceiling with skylights. Three-quarter Bath, plus Half Bath. In-unit Laundry with washer and dryer included. New in 2020:  electric subpanel, carpet, and garbage disposal.  Elevator access to other floors. Relax in the pool, hot tub, and sauna. Big party room with lots of space for family gatherings. Heated, underground parking garage.***Rentals require 2 year owner occupancy first.***

Recently sold: $240,000. This home is a Real Estate Owned (REO)/Post Foreclosure. Once a lender has foreclosed on a property it is soon put up for public auction. If bids fall short of the asking price the bank will buy back the home and attempt to sell it on the open market. However, lenders are not real estate agents, meaning that they will often accept offers 30 to 60 percent less than market value!

description: Recently sold: $325,000. A perfect blend of old and new are present in this lovely Lauderdale home. The original portion of the home welcomes you via the inviting front porch where you enter a charming living room with original woodwork and hardwood floors. The upper level features two bedrooms and a full bath. The addition portion features a master bedroom with bathroom, and a large family room, over a 2-car attached garage with direct access to the home. A gracious eat-in kitchen features ample cooking and dining space as well as french doors that lead to a large patio with pergola. An oversize, flat backyard has space for entertaining and gardening. A separate 2-car garage with workshop frame the back of the lot. Room to add an egress window and 4th bed down where there is currently a ¾ bath. Minutes from DT Minneapolis and St. Paul as well as the U of M. Great neighborhood, Roseville schools. Do not miss this hidden gem!

Recently sold: $258,000. *** 3D Tour at: www.2849virginia.com ***

Beautiful 4 level home with many charming features! The main level is great for entertaining and features a spacious living room with a large window overlooking the park like front yard and dining room that opens to the kitchen with updated flooring and new stainless steel appliances.

Upstairs features 3 Bedrooms - all with hardwood floors and large closets and a beautiful full bathroom with new flooring! The lower level features a large family room with fireplace and new carpet, 4th bedroom and ¾ bath with new flooring.

The lower level walks out to an amazing wooded backyard with maintenance free fencing, large deck with sauna and garden shed.

Don't miss the lower level storage room!
